column10:
Fairly decent, fine/fun gameplay
Still many issues, still toxic vibe, still unbalanced maps

After playing 300 hrs more, none of my issues have been solved:
1. Terrible horse physics;
2. Weird spawn mechanism, often you have 25+ masons and 10- agathians;
3. Poor server quality. Low tick, often laggy, sometimes the server crashes and kicks everyone out of the game.

Best online medieval war simulator.

Pros:
 - Combat is extremely good;
 - Graphics are nice;
 - Customization is nice.

Cons:
 - Team balancing is horrendous, almost every match is a stomp one way or the other;
 - Some game modes are just plain bad;
 - Not a lot of players.
